        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-4">
          COMPLETE ASSUMPTION OF ALL TRAVEL RISKS
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-4">
          BY USING THIS WEBSITE AND BOOKING ANY TOUR, YOU ACKNOWLEDGE AND VOLUNTARILY ASSUME ALL RISKS INCLUDING:
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Physical Risks & Injury</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-gray-800">
              <li>Death or serious bodily injury from any cause</li>
              <li>Accidents during activities (hiking, swimming, boating, etc.)</li>
              <li>Falls, drowning, or equipment failure</li>
              <li>Vehicle accidents (buses, boats, cars, aircraft)</li>
              <li>Animal attacks or insect/snake bites</li>
              <li>Exposure to extreme weather or environmental conditions</li>
              <li>Altitude sickness, dehydration, or sun exposure</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Health & Medical Risks</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-gray-800">
              <li>Medical emergencies with no immediate access to care</li>
              <li>Inadequate medical facilities in remote locations</li>
              <li>Food poisoning or waterborne illnesses</li>
              <li>Allergic reactions or pre-existing condition complications</li>
              <li>Infectious diseases or pandemics</li>
              <li>Mental health impacts from traumatic events</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Security & Political Risks</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-gray-800">
              <li>Terrorism, war, or civil unrest</li>
              <li>Crime including theft, assault, or kidnapping</li>
              <li>Government actions or border closures</li>
              <li>Detention or legal issues in foreign jurisdictions</li>
              <li>Changes in visa or entry requirements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Natural Disasters & Force Majeure</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-gray-800">
              <li>Earthquakes, tsunamis, or volcanic eruptions</li>
              <li>Floods, hurricanes, or severe storms</li>
              <li>Avalanches, landslides, or rockfalls</li>
              <li>Wildfires or extreme temperatures</li>
              <li>Any "Act of God" or force majeure event</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Financial & Service Risks</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-gray-800">
              <li>Tour cancellations or significant changes</li>
              <li>Tour operator bankruptcy or business failure</li>
              <li>Hidden fees or unexpected costs</li>
              <li>Substandard accommodations or services</li>
              <li>Loss of deposits or prepayments</li>
              <li>Currency fluctuations or payment issues</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
